msgid "Scan Rendered URL"
msgstr "掃描已渲染網址"

#: includes/class-admin.php:159
msgid "Fetches one rendered HTML response and stores findings. Use Freego for browser-authoritative validation."
msgstr "擷取一個已渲染的 HTML 回應並儲存發現項目。瀏覽器權威驗證仍請使用 Freego。"

#: includes/class-admin.php:161
msgid "Scan URL"
msgstr "掃描網址"

#: includes/class-admin.php:165
msgid "Repair Mode"
msgstr "修補模式"

#: includes/class-admin.php:169
msgid "Target level"
msgstr "目標等級"

#: includes/class-admin.php:175
msgid "Aggressive fake-value repair"
msgstr "積極假值修補"

#: includes/class-admin.php:176
msgid "When enabled, missing required attributes receive fallback values across Freego-covered elements. Existing valid values are not overwritten. Review markers are still added so semantic cleanup remains traceable."
msgstr "啟用後，Freego 涵蓋元素若缺少必要屬性，會補上 fallback 值。既有有效值不會被覆寫，且仍會加入審查標記，讓語意修正可追蹤。"

#: includes/class-admin.php:178
msgid "Delete plugin data when uninstalling"
msgstr "解除安裝時刪除外掛資料"

#: includes/class-admin.php:179
msgid "When enabled, uninstalling the plugin deletes the issue table, plugin options, cached update data, and Freego attachment metadata. Deactivation never deletes data."
msgstr "啟用後，解除安裝外掛會刪除問題資料表、外掛選項、快取更新資料與 Freego 附件 metadata。停用外掛永遠不會刪除資料。"

#: includes/class-admin.php:180
msgid "Save repair mode"
msgstr "儲存修補模式"

#: includes/class-admin.php:183
msgid "Rule Automation Split"
msgstr "規則自動化分類"

#: includes/class-admin.php:209
msgid "Issue Workflow"
msgstr "問題處理流程"

#: includes/class-admin.php:210
msgid "Open items are not automatically claimed as compliant. Mark them reviewed only after semantic or engineering confirmation."
msgstr "未處理項目不會自動宣稱合規。請在語意或工程確認後，才標記為已審查。"

#: includes/class-admin.php:213
msgid "No issues match the current filter."
msgstr "沒有符合目前篩選條件的問題。"

